body.name: Gizoon 45.5" Dining Table Set for 4, Kitchen Table Set with 2 Benches, Dining Room Table Set with Metal Frame & MDF Board, Space-Saving Dinette for Kitchen, Dining Room -Grey
features: 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦【Dining Table Set for 4】Kitchen table with bench comes complete with a spacious table(45.5 x 30.4 x 30.1 inches) and 2 ergonomic benches(41.1 x 18.4 x 12.1 inches each), the desktop is spacious enough, and easily accommodates 4 people dining, providing space for the whole family to enjoy the party. The weight capacity of this Space-Saving Dinette: Every bench:550 lbs; Table:330 lbs.

🏡【Space Saving Design】This kitchen dining table with benches is very compact to take up little space for storage. Slide the bench seats seamlessly under the table when not in use, which maximizes space while maintaining aesthetic appeal. It can also avoid unexpected tripping when delivering cuisine dishes to the dining table. It is a great solution for small spaces like small condos, small kitchens, and studio apartments.

💎【Sturdy Construction】Our dining room table set for 4 features a thick MDF board on the tabletop and the seats provide ample support and have an attractive wood grain finish. Splashproof treated surface easy to maintain. The surface of the steel pipe is painted with baking paint, which not only increases rust resistance but also increases stability. The sturdy triangular crossbars on the table and benches provide extra support.

💐【Modern & Stylish Style】The design of this small kitchen table is simple but it is classic and will never be out of date. The surface of the tabletop and benchtop has a unique wood grain, with the smooth lines making the kitchen table and chairs set appear bright. This kitchen table with bench is available in 3 colors with a natural wooden look, adds a sense of modernity and elegance, and is perfect for any decoration style in your home.

✔️【Perfect for Many Occasions】You can place your bread, tea, Coffee, etc on the kitchen table set enjoying a good time with your family and friends, feeling the beauty and warmth of life. The kitchen dining table set can also be used as a computer desk, study desk, writing desk, or breakfast nook, perfectly used in the kitchen, dining room, living room, party room, restaurant, bar, etc.

🛠️【Simple Assembly】 All pieces and instructions come in 1 box and are packaged well for transit purposes. This table and chair set comes with clear assembly instructions, all parts are clearly labeled, takes only 20 minutes to complete the set-up with the manual, or just with your common sense. Simple assembly beyond imagination. Any questions please contact us. GizoonTeam always keeps online.

🚨【Silicone Protection Device】In order to create a safe environment for you to use, the product is upgraded. It has 12 silicone protection devices. Suitable for placing on the edge of tables and benches to increase cushioning and prevent bruises. You can choose whether to install the device.

reviews.reviewText: So we wanted something that didn't take up a lot of space and this is perfect. It fits 4 comfortably. We love the benches. It's not very heavy but sturdy. Not woobly at all. It was one of the easiest assembly's I've done.Most importantly I want to point out how this company went above and beyond. FedEx lost our package (even though we paid $50 shipping) and denied our claim. They made me contact the seller of this product and the company immediately replaced the table with a brand new one. This says a lot about the company because it was not their fault the product was lost by FedEx.As for FedEx they get a 0 out of 5 star review because they are the worst shipping company. Every package we get from them is late or lost. Get it together FedEx. But to the seller of this product. Thank you so much for taking care of us!Highly recommend.
